      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Yes, MU is a valid Scrabble word worth 4 points in both TWL and SOWPODS. It's the 12th letter of the Greek alphabet (Μ, μ), and M(3) gives it double the scoring power of its cousin NU (2pts). If you're learning Greek alphabet words for Scrabble, MU should be in your arsenal right after XI (9pts) and before NU.</p>

