        <p class="text-sm text-green-300 font-semibold mb-3">4 points · M=3, U=1 · 12th letter of the Greek alphabet</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Valid in both TWL and SOWPODS. MU (Μ, μ) represents the micro- prefix in science (μg, μm) and is used in statistics, physics, and mathematics. In Scrabble, it's a reliable M-dump that scores better than most 2-letter words.</p>
      </div>

