        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-800/40">
          <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-1">NU — 2 pts (Lowest)</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">N(1)+U(1). Only use when no other play exists. Half of MU's value.</p>
        </div>
